            <li>leverage: one subscribe interface, N consumers</li>
            <li>InstanceStore interface shrinks =E2=80=94 emitter and telem=
etry option gone</li>
            <li>tests assert spans by subscribing, not by faking telemetry =
inside the store</li>
            <li>three adapters justify the seam =E2=80=94 it's real, not hy=
pothetical</li>
          </ul>
